T1  - Managerial Regret and Inventory Pricing
AU  - Li, Meng
AU  - Liu, Yan
Y1  - 2022/02/08
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2022/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2021.4073
